            {
              "enText": "<b>Lesson 4 • Talking about manufacturing</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "Mike and Dan work for Swift Shoes, a manufacturer of sneakers. Mike is in charge of manufacturing. Dan is trying to push Mike to get some new shoes ready quickly."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Dan:</b> We've decided to launch our new spring shoe on April 20th."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Mike:</b> We're still trying to <b>work out the kinks</b> in our manufacturing process. Our factory in China is having trouble with the soles."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Dan:</b> I know that, Mike. But you've still got three months. It should be plenty of time."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Mike:</b> It could take another six months to <b>fine-tune</b> our manufacturing process."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Dan:</b> Well, we don't have that much time. <b>No ifs, ands, or buts</b> we need to launch on April 20th."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Mike:</b> <b>Just for the record</b>, I think we're <b>cutting it a little close</b>. I recommend we launch on July 20th instead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Dan:</b> We can't. We've already decided on the <b>tagline</b>: \"Spring into spring with Swift's new spring shoe.\""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Mike:</b> It's time for a <b>reality check</b>. I'm telling you we might not be ready by April 20th, and you're telling me we have to be because of a <b>tagline</b>?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Dan:</b> Mike, now's the time to <b>step up to the plate</b> and <b>get the job done</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Mike:</b> Mike: Well, I'm going to be <b>working down to the wire</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Dan:</b> Just <b>do whatever it takes</b>. Just make sure we've got a million pairs of shoes in inventory by the April 20th deadline."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Mike:</b> I'm going to have to run the factories <b>24/7</b>. That's going to be a lot of overtime pay."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Dan:</b> <b>At the end of the day</b>, a little extra expense doesn't matter. We just want those shoes ready by April 20th."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
